						               													<description>From the box - &amp;#10;Hold on to your blue chips! The MONOPOLY Game and the Berkshire Hathaway Company have cornered the market on fun with a twist on America's favorite board game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The epic MONOPOLY Brand property trading game dedicates this &amp;quot;Diamond Edition&amp;quot; to the world of investing and Berkshire Hathaway collectors. Showcasing a variety of the most desirable and highly sought after properties on the market, players can buy, sell and trade to own them all! This exclusive collector's edition comes complete with custom pewter tokens representing the unique acquisitions within the Berkshire Hathaway family. Keep the entrepreneur spirit alive by acquiring controlling interest in investment properties and continue to grow your assets by expanding with additional buildings. The game board properties you'll be vying for incorporate many of the Berkshire Hathaway companies including GEICO, Fruit of the Loom, Dairy Queen and Borsheim's. Control the board to become CEO of Berkshire Hathaway!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The pewter tokens are: a Gecko, cowboy boot, airplane, ice cream cone, sofa and a diamond ring.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
